un-time evaluation. A static expression is required to initialize `thread` data.  \n  \n## Example  \n The following sample generates C2483.  \n  \n```  \n// C2483.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \n__declspec(thread) struct A {  \n   A(){}  \n   ~A(){}  \n} aa;   // C2483 error  \n  \n__declspec(thread) struct B {} b;   // OK  \n```  \n  \n## See Also  \n [thread](../../cpp/thread.md)"}